Usage:
  cape submission new <scenario> <language> <version> <github-handle>

Examples:
  cape submission new fibonacci Aiken 1.1.17 KtorZ
  cape submission new fibonacci Plinth 1.52.0.0 Unisay

Notes:
  - All arguments are required; if any are missing, the command fails.
  - Folder name will be <language>_<version>_<github-handle>.
  - Scenario must exist as scenarios/<scenario>.md.
  - Language: letters/digits/hyphens only (no spaces).
  - Version: digits, dots and hyphens (e.g., 1.52.0.0 or 1.1.17).
  - GitHub handle: 1-39 chars, alnum and hyphens, cannot start/end with '-'.
